        <span class="label">06 · Fit</span>
        <h2>Best for.<br/><em>And not for.</em></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="yesno">
        <div class="col yes">
          <h3>Best for</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Consumer brands (DTC + omnichannel) at $5M–$200M annual revenue.</li>
            <li>Operators who've tried a one-off AI tool that quietly stopped getting used.</li>
            <li>Founders or VPs who want a defensible AI strategy their team can run after we leave.</li>
            <li>Teams already using Shopify, Klaviyo, Triple Whale (or willing to migrate).</li>
            <li>Brands at a 1.5x+ growth posture — the operating system pays back when volume scales.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col no">
          <h3>Where we'll say no</h3>
          <ul>
